body: To complete this form you will need the form TE3 Order for recovery of unpaid penalty charge.

components.html: ### If you have any difficulty completing this form you can contact the Traffic Enforcement Centre on 0300 123 1059. ###

heading: TE9 - Witness statement - unpaid penalty charge
lede: You  must file this statement by the date shown on the Order for  recovery (form TE3)
